    "The domain-wise organization of SDN is adding a novel direction to the desired system.",
    "The controller of the SDN is incorporated into the Blockchain approach, which can be capable of providing a high bond of security in the proposed system efficiently.",
    "Moreover, the Blockchain network is used not only to store public and private patient data but also to store healthcare information.",
